#           #[arg(short = '4', long)] ipv4: bool,
#           #[arg(short = '6', long)] ipv6: bool }
#
#   This entry is the Rust=176 leader bump that **OPENS Axis 121
#   (DNS / IETF RFC-1035 + DoT / DoH / DoQ name-resolution
#   protocol)** at 1/0/0 following R1060 _transcribe-chords
#   (TS-Node=175 CLOSED Axis 120 MIDI at 1/1/1 triple-175 +
#   113th axis closed).  Go=176 continuation on deck for R1062
#   via the canonical Go DNS library `miekg/dns` (Miek Gieben's
#   reference pure-Go DNS implementation — THE Go DNS library,
#   used by CoreDNS, Cloudflare's authoritative servers,
#   Mastodon's federation resolver, DigitalOcean's DNS API,
#   and countless others).  TS-Node=176 closing pair at R1063
#   via the canonical Node.js DNS library `dns2` (Pollux Lin's
